<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-22 00:57 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1372 &Cx1f; ttx-z
r s BC-BBA-RANGERS-TWINS-TEX     06-22 0687
