</P>
<P>
   BUSINESS/FINANCE (``f'' category)
</P>
<P>
   CAREER-COLUMN (San Francisco) _ Suppose you have an employee who
is nearly as talented in your field as Tiger Woods is in his. Could
you bring out the best in that worker? Probably not. Sorry to say,
but most bosses are better suited to managing mediocrity than
promoting talent. By DAVE MURPHY.
</P>
<P>
   CALIF-ECONOMY (San Francisco) _ California's economy is booming
thanks to a rebound in international markets that led to a
double-digit gain in exports and the now-familiar creation of new
wealth, once again bringing a windfall for workers in the form of
jobs, higher wages and more security, according to a respected
economic forecast. By CHRISTAIN BERTHELSEN.
