</P>
<P>
   ARABICA-FILM-REVIEW (Undated) _ As ``100 Percent Arabica''
demonstrates, many social tensions followed Algerian immigrants
from their homeland and into their impoverished neighborhoods on
the outskirts of Paris. Reviewed by Stephen Holden.
