<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-22 18:06 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1943 &Cx1f; tad-z
u p BC-POLL-0623-COX     06-22 0777
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-POLL-0623-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    GORE'S ``MOVING PICTURES'' HEADED IN WRONG DIRECTION
 &HT;    By SCOTT SHEPARD
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
