<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-22 18:52 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1988 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e BC-R-APPLES-LOSANGELES-4     06-22 1361
