<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    MICROSOFT UNVEILS NET-BASED STRATEGY FOR THE FUTURE
 &HT;    Moving in (a) national and (f) financial categories.
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   REDMOND, Wash. _ With an antitrust sword hanging over its head,
Microsoft Corp. on Thursday sought to convert itself into a
dominant force in the next generation of advanced Internet
services.
</P>
<P>
   ``You could say it's a 'bet the company' thing,'' Bill Gates,
