<DOCNO> NYT20000622.0278 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-22 19:07 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2002 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e BC-OLD-THEATERS-ART-3RDT     06-22 0610
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-OLD-THEATERS-ART-3RDTAKE-NYT </SLUG>
  
 UNDATED: their history.''  
<TEXT>
<P>
