<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GRAHAM-EXECUTION-1600(2ndTake)-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
GRAHAM EXECUTED AFTER DAY OF DELAYS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
 
HUNTSVILLE, Texas: the death chamber. 
Bobby Hanners, Lambert's grandson, was joined in a separate room by
crime-victims rights activist Dianne Clements and family friend
Rick Sandford.
